  body
    section.brand
      .container
        img.logo(src="/images/augur_logo_600.png" alt="augur logo")
        h4.funds-raised <b><span class="amount-raised">0.0000</span> BTC</b> in funds raised
        .timer
        h4.sale-starts until sale starts on <b>Monday, August 17th, 12:00 PM EST</b>
    section.action
      .container
        if user
          h2 Hello, <b>#{ user.fullName }</b>
          h4 You own <b>#{ repPercentage }% Reputation</b> after spending <b>#{ btcBalance } BTC</b>
          if ethereumAddress
            p.ethereum-address Your <b>Ethereum</b> address is <b>#{ ethereumAddress }</b> <a onclick="editEthereumAddress();">change</a>
            form.center-block(method='post', role='form', style="display: none;")
              .input-group
                input.form-control(name="ethereumAddress", value="#{ ethereumAddress }")
                span.input-group-btn
                  button.btn.btn-default(type="submit") Save
                  button.btn.btn-default(type="button", onclick="cancelEdit()") Cancel
          else
            form.center-block(method='post', role='form')
              .input-group
                input.form-control(name="ethereumAddress", placeholder="Enter your Ethereum address" data-toggle="tooltip-left" title="Warning! Make sure this is an Ethereum address you have the privatekey to (meaning: it's not an exchange address). You'll need it for reporting!")
                span.input-group-btn
                  button.btn.btn-default(type="submit") Save
          .row
            .col-sm-12
              if false
                p
                  img.qrcode.center-block(src="#{ qrCode }")
                p.buy-uri
                  a(href="#{ buyUri }" data-toggle="tooltip-left" title="Send Bitcoin to this address and you'll get rep in proportion to the amount") #{ btcAddress }
                p.or <b>or</b>
                p.shifty-io
                  a(onclick="shapeshift_click(this, event);" href="https://shapeshift.io/shifty.html?destination=#{ btcAddress }&amp;output=BTC")
                    img.ss-button(src="https://shapeshift.io/images/shifty/xs_dark_altcoins.png")
              else
                h4.check-back Check back here when our sale starts to buy in and help bring Augur to the world
              .logout
                a(href="/logout") logout
        else
          h2 Be a part of <b>making history</b>
          .row
            .col-sm-6
              .intro
                <p>To continue funding our ambitious project of the World's first decentralized, prediction market, we are selling Reputation in Augur.</p>
                <p>Reputation and it's owners are what compose the distributed oracle and determine the outcome of market events.  See the video below for a brief introduction of how this works and <a href="http://www.augur.net/blog/what-is-reputation">our blog post</a> for a more in-depth look.</p>
            .col-sm-5.col-sm-offset-1
              p.login
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href="/login") Login and get started!
              p.disclaimer By logging in you agree to <a href="/legal">the terms</a> of the Augur crowd-sale</p>
    section.video
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            <h3>Reputation in Augur</h3>
            .wrapper
              .video
                iframe(src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sCms-snzHk4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen)


    section.fund-management
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12 <h3>Fund management</h3>
        .row
          .col-md-12
            <p>All proceeds received from Augur software sale are under control of a multi-sig wallet, that will require co-signature of at least 2 signers out of 3 signers listed below.</p>
            .row.holder-people
              .col-sm-4
                .member-team
                  a(href="#")
                    span.img(data-picture data-alt="illustration")
                      <span data-src="/images/teamMembers/augurfoundation.png"></span>
                      <span data-src="/images/teamMembers/augurfoundation.png" data-media="(min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.5), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.5), (min-resolution: 192dpi)"></span>
                      noscript
                        <img src="/images/img/teamMembers/augurfoundation.png" alt="illustration" />

                  <h4><a href="#">Forecast Foundation</a></h4>
                  <p class="position">Foundation, Augur</p>
                  <p class="role"><strong>Fund Reciever</strong> </p>
              .col-sm-4
                .member-team
                  a(href="#")
                    span.img(data-picture data-alt="illustration")
                      <span data-src="/images/teamMembers/bitgo.png"></span>
                      <span data-src="/images/teamMembers/bitgo.png" data-media="(min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.5), (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.5), (min-resolution: 192dpi)"></span>
                      noscript
                        <img src="img/teamMembers/bitgo.png" alt="illustration" />
                  <h4><a href="#">BitGo</a></h4>
                  <p class="position">Multi-Sig Provider</p>
                  <p class="role"><strong>Key Manager</strong></p>

    section.fund-allocation
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            <h3>Fund allocation</h3>
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            <p>The proceeds from this software sale will be primarily used for making sure Augur developers are incentivized to constantly improve the product beyond their initial release. Specific costs are found from the development of the network infrastructure, paying for servers (for our blockchain.info style solution for people who don't want to run the full client), paying for bandwidth, marketing, as well as legal and business development.</p>
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            div
              <h6>Development Compensation &amp; Ops</h6>
              .progress
                .progress-bar(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="75%" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 75%;")
                  <span>75%</span>
            div
              <h6>Legal Contingency Fund</h6>
              .progress
                .progress-bar(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="15" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 15%;")
                  <span>15%</span>
            div
              <h6>Marketing & Community Outreach</h6>
              .progress
                .progress-bar(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="10" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 10%;")
                  <span>10%</span>

    section.token-management
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            <h3>Token Issuance</h3>
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            <p>Reputation (REP) is the token that allows an individual to report on the outcome of events (and receive part of the system’s trading fees as compensation.) All 11,000,000 REP tokens that will ever exist will during the software sale will be distributed at the end of the software sale. The distribution of tokens will be constantly shifting in real-time as new participants buy into the system using our novel “Live-Action” token distribution software to create a true free market pricing.
            </p>
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            div
              <h6>Public Software Sale</h6>
              .progress
                .progress-bar(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="80%" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 80%;")
                  <span>80%</span>
            div
              <h6>Early Angels & Founding Team</h6>
              .progress
                .progress-bar(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="16" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 16%;")
                  <span>16%</span>
            div
              <h6>Forecast Foundation</h6>
              .progress
                .progress-bar(role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="4" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 4%;")
                <span>4%</span

